right after them

1. *Prestanite* da se prepirate! (Stop arguing!)
2. Oni su *prestali* da se druže nakon što su se svađali. (They stopped hanging out after they had a fight.)
3. Oboje moraju da *prestanu* da se ljute. (They both have to stop being mad.)
4. Ona je *prestala* da govori kada ga je videla. (She stopped talking when she saw him.)
5. *Prestanite* da me zezate! (Stop teasing me!)